public class XYStepRenderer
extends XYLineAndShapeRenderer
implements XYItemRenderer, java.lang.Cloneable, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable, java.io.Serializable

Line/Step item renderer for an XYPlot. This class draws lines between data points, only allowing horizontal or vertical lines (steps).

Author:
Roger Studner
